    "ELVISHLY": "In an elvish manner. Sir W. Scott.",
    "ELWAND": "See Ellwand.",
    "ELYSIAN": "Pertaining, or the abode of the blessed after death; hence,yielding the highest pleasures; exceedingly delightful; beatific.\"Elysian shades.\" Massinger. \"Elysian age.\" Beattie.This life of mortal breath Is but a suburb of the life elysian.Longfellow.",
