    "EMPEROR": "The sovereign or supreme monarch of an empire; -- a title ofdignity superior to that of king; as, the emperor of Germany or ofAustria; the emperor or Czar of Russia. Emperor goose (Zoöl.), alarge and handsome goose (Philacte canagica), found in Alaska.-- Emperor moth (Zoöl.), one of several large and beautiful bombycidmoths, with transparent spots on the wings; as the American Cecropiamoth (Platysamia cecropia), and the European species (Saturniapavonia).-- Emperor paper. See under Paper.-- Purple emperor (Zoöl.), a large, strong British butterfly(Apatura iris).",
