    "ENTHUSIAST": "One moved or actuated by enthusiasm; as: (a) One who imagineshimself divinely inspired, or possessed of some special revelation; areligious madman; a fanatic. (b) One whose mind is wholly possessedand heated by what engages it; one who is influenced by a peculiar;fervor of mind; an ardent and imaginative person.Enthusiasts soon understand each other. W. Irving.",
