    "EXCAVATE": "To dig out and remove, as earth.The material excavated was usually sand. E. L. Corthell.Excavating pump, a kind of dredging apparatus for excavating underwater, in which silt and loose material mixed with water are drawn upby a pump. Knight.",
    "EXCAVATOR": "One who, or that which, excavates or hollows out; a machine, asa dredging machine, or a tool, for excavating.",
